==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|frm|en}} {{term|roan|lang=frm}}, probably from {{etyl|es|en}} {{term|roano|lang=es}}, from {{etyl|osp|en}} {{term|raudano|lang=osp}}, itself probably of {{etyl|gem|en}} origin (cf. Gothic ''raudan'', accusative of {{term|𐍂𐌰𐌿𐌸𐍃||red|tr=rauþs|lang=got}}.

===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

